NAME
     9x more scum & rats than rio. Just say NEIN.

DESCRIPTION
     9x is a scummy X11 window manager. A rat infested rio rip-off.  It
     provides far more than you bargained for.  Do 9 things and do them
     poorly.

OPTIONS
     -v  Erase computer. Weep.

MOUSE
   Run Button
     Hover  Launcher.

   Launcher
     Button 1  Launch.

     Button 3  Sweep.

   Window Tabs
     Hover     Focus.

     Button 1  Maximize.

     Button 2  Delete.

     Button 3  Re-Sweep.

   Desktop Buttons
     Button 1  Switch to Desktop.

     Button 2  Window to Desktop.

     Button 3  Follow Window to Desktop.

   Status Area (Battery/Clock)
     Any Button  Sweep.

   Window Borders
     Button 1     Resize.

     Button 2     Delete.

     Button 3     Move.

     Doubleclick  Tile.

   Root Window
     Any Button  Sweep.

KEYBOARD
     F11  Fullscreen.

CUSTOMIZATION
     Read the goddamn src(1) you filthy heathen.

SEE ALSO
     X(7), xterm(1)

AUTHORS
     Toby Slight

